## Next Steps for Activation

To activate Web Analytics in production:
1. Deploy this project to Vercel (`vercel deploy`)
2. Navigate to the project's Analytics section in the Vercel dashboard
3. Click the "Enable" button to activate Web Analytics
4. After deployment and user visits, analytics data will appear in the dashboard

## Files Modified
- `package.json` - Added @vercel/analytics dependency
- `package-lock.json` - Updated with new dependency tree
- `src/app/layout.tsx` - Added Analytics component

## Technical Notes
- Analytics component is lightweight and doesn't impact page load performance
- Data collection is GDPR-compliant and privacy-focused
- No additional environment variables or configuration needed
- Works automatically on Vercel deployments
